      <title>印度希望央行提供 120 亿美元的资金来援助预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/india-eyes-12-billion-bonanza-from-central-bank-aiding-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经济学家表示，印度央行预计将向联邦政府支付高达 1 万亿卢比（120 亿美元）的股息，此举将增加新德里的国库并有助于实现其预算赤字目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/india-eyes-12-billion-bonanza-from-central-bank-aiding-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 23:31:00 GMT</pubDate>
