      <title>首席财务官表示，随着降息停滞，XP的增长将“不那么积极”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/xp-to-grow-less-aggressively-while-rate-cuts-stall-cfo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西投资公司 XP Inc. 首席财务官布鲁诺·康斯坦丁周二表示，预计其零售收入和净新资金将继续增长，但“增长幅度不及预期”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/xp-to-grow-less-aggressively-while-rate-cuts-stall-cfo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 21:30:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>顶级基金因降息押注更青睐新西兰债券而非澳元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/top-fund-prefers-kiwi-bonds-over-aussie-debt-on-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位表现最佳的基金经理表示，新西兰政府债务看起来比澳大利亚政府债务更具吸引力，因为该国央行可能很快就会开始降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/top-fund-prefers-kiwi-bonds-over-aussie-debt-on-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 21:12:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行拉加德预计六月降息，通胀“受到控制”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/ecb-s-lagarde-sees-june-rate-cut-with-inflation-under-control</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，下个月可能会降息，因为消费者价格增长的快速增长目前已基本得到遏制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/ecb-s-lagarde-sees-june-rate-cut-with-inflation-under-control</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
